    {
      "id": "8eaa0163-bd38-459e-b1e0-11e3b7634074",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The model, Attn-ANN combines weightings on time and feature dimensions to identify significance of lectures and learning activities. The model seems to outperform convencional algorithms at the task of early prediction of student performance. Moreover, an analysis of the netwroks decisions shows potential for synergy between model and educational experts. ",
